        <span id="BookReviewTitle" class="BookReviewTitle">The Evolution of Useful Things: How Everyday Artifacts-From Forks and Pins to Paper Clips and Zippers-Came to be as They are</span>
        <div class="ItemDetail">By
          <span id="Authors">HENRY PETROSKI</span></div>
